content.rendered:
Directed by Vivek Athreya

Star Nani (Sundar Prasad). Nazriya Nazim (Leela Thomas). V.K. Naresh (Mr. Sastry, Sundar’s Father). Azhagam Perumal (Mr. Thomas, Leela’s Father). Nadia Moidu (Leela’s Mother). Tanvi Ram (Pushpa, Leela’s sister). Rohini (Sundar’s Mother). Venkatesh Maha (Joseph). Harshavardhan (Sundar’s Boss). Anupama Parameswaran (Soumya). Sai Ronak (Vamsi). Srikanth Iyengar (Astrologer). Rahul Ramakrishna (Doctor). Pruthvi (Sundar’s Uncle)

Written by Vivek Athreya

Language Telugu

Producers Chiranjeevi Pedamallu. Y. Ravi Shankar. Naveen Yerneni

Production Mythri Movie Makers
